body_html: I am closing this bug due to lack of recent activity. For future searchwes, the original poster posted that they were using Mac OS 10.6. which was subsumed by Mac OS Lion in 2011. libc++ was not included in Mac OS Snow Leopward because Apple had not switched to Clang and libc++ yet. Our binaries are for a single version of Mac OS (El Capitan currently). For the subsequent posters, please file a new bug with your relevant system details.
